Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.95,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}[Dunia Matahari]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:33.69,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}[Sekolah Walrus]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:30.70,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}[Bersambung]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Berlarilah\Nsampai tiba di sana ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Sampai perasaanku\Ntersampaikan kepadamu ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}[One Piece\NEpisode 1170]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Lautan yang begitu biru dan jernih ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Serpihan keajaiban yang bertebaran ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Jumlahnya tidak terhitung lagi ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Kita pun dipertemukan karenanya ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Perjalanan yang panjang\Nlangkah kaki tidak terhenti ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Titik akhir masih belum terlihat juga ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.38,0:00:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Namun kita pasti akan\Nmelompati segala rintangan ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Demi melihat senyuman itu ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Jika tenggelam dalam kebingungan\Ntidak akan bisa menerangi jalan di depan ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.26,0:00:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Mengolah kelemahanmu dengan teliti\Nhingga ia berubah menjadi nutrisi ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.07,0:01:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Kita yang berjuang sekuat tenaga\Ntetap saja ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Belum ada yang berubah ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Berlarilah ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Sampai tiba di sana\Nsampai perasaan tersampaikan kepadamu ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.27,0:01:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Meski belum menjadi legenda\Nmemangnya kenapa! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Peta itu bersinar terang\Nsuatu hari kita menoleh sambil tersenyum ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Kini tidak lagi bimbang\Npara pejuang teruslah maju ke depan ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harta karun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.53,0:01:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya kosong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan Ruang Harta Karun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini ruang peti harta.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penipu. Payah sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan salahkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini adalah kastel tanpa penghuni.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja jadi incaran pencuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, coba kalian lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kunci gembok. Baguslah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu-satunya benda yang tidak diinginkan\Npara pencuri yang kemari adalah ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Merebut Kunci, Luffy VS Scopper Gaban.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan para penjahat\Ntidak ingin Loki dibebaskan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cobalah rebut dari tanganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya-san, apa yang hendak kau lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kau membawa kami ke sini\Nuntuk memberikan kunci itu kepada kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengapa harus merebutnya\Ndari tangan Paman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikan saja langsung padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan banyak omong kosong,\Nayo hadapi aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ataukah kau tidak sanggup merebutnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahku adalah suku manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah ayahmu adalah manusia?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dulu dia seorang bajak laut, prajurit\Nyang tidak kalah dari prajurit Elbaph.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, suami lebih muda dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:04:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bilang hanya dirinya yang menua, lalu\Nmerajuk dan tidak mau menikah denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini salah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Paman, aku harus segera pergi\Nke tempat Loki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.78,0:04:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga harus kembali melanjutkan pesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pesta memang cukup menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, kemari dan rebutlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama sekali tidak masuk akal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Haki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tu... tunggu, Ya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Pak Tua! Kau mengejutkanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Topi Jerami ini bagus juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini lebih cocok untukmu daripada helm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini harta berharga\Nyang dititipkan Shanks padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikan kunci itu padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dititipkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan diberikan padamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh pria yang pelit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh! Bukan itu maksudnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak tahu apa-apa,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jangan bilang Shanks pelit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau cukup mampu membantah, ya, bocah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa-apaan ini. Dasar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu... Nami-tasso.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lawannya adalah Ya-san,\Nbahkan Luffy-tasso juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapak?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luffy, lekas menghindar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yasotakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sakit sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau punya rekan yang baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oi, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo maju, Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar-benar putih.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Siapkan dirimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menyerah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa-apaan ini, tua bangka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan kesal begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya bercanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tadi mau membunuh orang,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mana bisa disebut bercanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula tidak mati, apa hubungannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya apa-apaan ini, dasar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat baik-baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kunci yang kalian cari
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sudah ada di tangan kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lu... Luffy-tasso, dengarkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, pria ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan terburu-buru, Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat kalian meninggalkan pulau ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalau Elbaph masih selamat,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}baru temui aku lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atas dasar apa?\NSiapa yang masih mau menemuimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, dasar berengsek!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah memberi tahu kami\Nposisi kuncinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat tinggal untuk selamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu sudah aku pahami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, Shanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pikir aku akan dengan mudah percaya\Npada bocah itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terserah kau mau bagaimana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Gaban.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat lari!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhenti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat lari.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memanjat pohon itu curang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Para anak laki-laki itu\Nsedang bermain kejar-kejaran lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selalu tidak pernah dewasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Guru, Guru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada sesuatu yang aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada bocah aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat sedikit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat lihat! Burung!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Burung.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Burung juga bukan hal aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, itu burung aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar-benar seperti khusus\Ndisiapkan untuk kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku panggil orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, aku sudah mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pergi ke sana memang tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari mana berangkatnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana Abyss-nya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena demikian,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}beri aku waktu satu jam lagi, bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana, sebenarnya di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, masih banyak persiapan\Nyang harus dilakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berganti pakaian dan sebagainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelompok Kesatria Dewa tidak mungkin
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pergi dengan telanjang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:18:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}[Kelompok Kesatria Dewa\N(Keluarga Shepherd) Saint Sommers]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ngomong-ngomong, bagaimana kabar hal itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku soal persediaan makanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu tidak bisa\Nmembiarkan para dewa kelaparan, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa? Ada apa?\N- Di mana, di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Gelombang pikirannya terputus-putus.\N- Di mana, di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Halo, bisa dengar?\N- Di mana, di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlambat. Aku akan terlambat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}[Kelompok Kesatria Dewa (Keluarga\NRimoshifu) Saint Rimoshifu Killingham]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benar-benar linglung setelah tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku disuruh ke mana tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat sedikit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berisik sekali, Killingham.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya pakailah baju dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, ke toilet dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh enggan menjadi tua.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Killingham?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sommers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Shamrock?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gunko juga ada di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.41,0:18:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian datang ke rumahku ada urusan apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini adalah Elbaph?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang bahkan akan ikut mengirimkan\Nsofa di kamarku juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, ini Negeri Raksasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pohon itu sungguh besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bala bantuan satu orang saja sudah cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau memanggil dua orang?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kau akan pulang, Komandan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu perintah dari atasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat ini kondisi Tanah Suci\Nmemang sangat parah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah rapat pemerintah dunia,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:19:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sudah benar-benar kacau balau.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shamrock, sebaiknya kau tetap pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ceritakanlah situasi dan misinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian datang ke negara\Nnon-anggota seperti ini mau apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa mau ziarah ke makam Harald?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menculik bocah-bocah ke Tanah Suci, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tepat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi bagaimana kalian mau melakukannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak-anak ini bertubuh begitu besar,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak bisa dimasukkan ke karung.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang tanpa tanda\Ntidak bisa melewati Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu hanya bisa, huff...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.79,0:21:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diangkut pakai kapal saja, huff...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bocah ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kata-katanya benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan kemampuan kalian...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita mainkan permainan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Berusaha keras membuka mata lebar-lebar\Nuntuk memastikan situasi di depan ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Otak penuh khayalan dan keputusasaan\Nentah kenapa selalu agak menyimpang ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:22:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Kenangan-kenangan buruk selalu\Nmuncul kembali dengan sangat jelas ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.11,0:22:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Memunguti kebosanan tidak berarti\Nrasanya hampir jadi orang lain ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.61,0:22:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Masa depan seperti apa\Nyang sebenarnya menjadi milikku ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Berdiri di sini dan sejauh apa pun\Nmencari tetap tidak terlihat ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Menentang angin dan robek ilusi salah\Nserta membuangnya ke celah takdir ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Orang-orang terus berputar dalam siklus\Nkenyataan yang begitu keras ini ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Hari esok begitu riuh hingga tidak ada\Nwaktu untuk berdoa akan segera tiba ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.12,0:22:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}♪ Lihat masa depan itu\Nkarena ia adalah milikku ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luffy dan Zoro membawa kunci\Nuntuk membebaskan Loki menuju Dunia Bawah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sana, yang mereka saksikan\Ndengan mata kepala sendiri
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah Loki yang penuh luka\Ndi sekujur tubuhnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat cengkeraman para penyusup\Nmakin mendekat,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Pangeran Terkutuk" yang terikat\Npada Pohon Harta Adam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.90,0:23:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apakah akhirnya\Nakan mendapatkan kebebasannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Episode selanjutnya, One Piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.84,0:23:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pendosa Besar Elbaph,\NLoki yang Membebaskan Dunia Bawah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.85,0:23:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}[Pendosa Besar Elbaph,\NLoki yang Membebaskan Dunia Bawah]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.84,0:23:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menjadi Raja Bajak Laut!
